gold: This statistic displays a ranking of the top ten Swedish influencers on Instagram ranked by the number of followers.
As of August 2017 , Anna Nyström ( annanystrom ) ranked first with 4.9 million followers and Thisis MansWorld ( thisisamans.world ) came in second with 2.1 million followers .
